title: Wooden Tooth Fairy Box Dropped Tooth Keepsake Storage Box for Boys and Girls Cute Lost Tooth Holder Toddler Teeth Case (1)
features: Cute Design: There is a cute 3D white tooth on the top of the tooth fairy box,and we carved grooves on the body of the wooden box to make it look more beautiful and delicate.

Dropped Tooth Storage Box: It could be used to keeping your baby's lost teeth and be placed under the pillow, wait for the tooth fairy to arrive. Parents can put the fallen teeth in the box as a growth gift for their children.

Material and Size: the baby teeth keepsake box is made of quality wood,reliable and solid, suitable for long-term lost teeth storage.The size is about 2 x 2 x 1.4 inches,it is lightweight and portable.

Childhood Memory: Let you kid know that losing a tooth is an exciting and proud moment because this is meaning growth.Each baby tooth is precious to the child,Keep the lost teeth in the box and preserve unforgettable growing up moments.

Gift for Kids: the tooth fairy keepsake container is suitable for kids in the changing tooth period, It would be an exquisite warm present in his growth life. Also, a great way to encourage good dental care.it also can be a lucky keepsake and be kept for years. Ideal gift for your daughter, friends' kids, family members in birthday party, baby shower and so on.
